{"tid":2463751,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"赤柱還柙人士一個晚餐要＄160/180","createTime":"2021-03-27T03:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T03:41:15.000Z","uid":52779,"like":95,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"f54dfe6d41d04750d7e30da1c51971587fd8e065","tid":2463751,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"洋蔥溝奶茶豬扒飯？ ！<br />\n其實更多人關心還柙人士的私飯問題。私飯愈來愈貴（赤柱：＄160/180一個晚餐），固然是問題；但又貴又質素差，更叫人氣憤。據悉私飯質素差，竟跟懲教的行政和職員的態度有關，只是私飯供夜商食咗死貓而已。<br />\n<br />\n近日赤柱監獄部分所員收到私飯後，發現飯盒打大風，餸菜被弄得橫七豎八。魚扒變魚蓉；蒸蛋變蛋蓉⋯總之就「你估佢唔到！」。一份好地地的餐，就俾懲教搞到一團糟！<br />\n<br />\n至於飲品，原來新來的保安組職員在抽樣檢查中，會將飲品粗暴地「過杯」（即係將原本裝奶茶嘅杯，倒到檸檬茶杯、檸檬茶杯就倒到阿華田杯，而過杯過程中液體四濺，一杯變三分二杯，通通扣底；而更難頂的是懲教並非完全將杯中飲品過到另一隻杯，會留番大約1/5在杯底，變相將至少兩種不同飲品溝埋&hellip;結果杯杯嘢都變成怪味兩溝。<br />\n<br />\n所員向懲教投訴飯盒或飲品有問題時，懲教會將問題轉移到飯商，表示是飯商在運送過程所致。飲品倒翻或飯盒溝飲品，例如洋蔥溝奶茶豬扒飯，要埋怨就請家屬直接向飯商投訴吧！家屬不知袖裡，自然照做如儀，懲教轉移視線成功！<br />\n<br />\n如此種種，多多少少跟47人有關。食肆做私飯多年，都未見過如此「痴線」及「好做唔做」。而最終目的不為甚麼，都是想令食私飯的所員「知難而退」，而轉食大棚飯。<br />\n<br />\n當我們眼見愈來愈多人選擇食大棚飯的時候，除了價錢貴之外，還有貴夾樣衰的問題，一切一切都有一雙幕後黑手在操盤。<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻 <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/148053572047302/posts/1636962729823038/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F148053572047302%2Fposts%2F1636962729823038%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=5c82714e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/148053572047302/posts/1636962729823038/?d=n</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdrn2a7aamL4adQmqVxLhyBGWHHadkpWV4wp6wM19ccjE?filename=ZxQ6AKV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZxQ6AKV.jpg&h=9982960e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c7060adbaf54e9ef50c1611a9afdeaa094543f0","tid":2463751,"uid":204231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae2f99e82fc3b7106905b82dfcd4b3de436d5b2","tid":2463751,"uid":157037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e711694dc4e31de8f1471a3b2fa5754aadfdaa03","tid":2463751,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52284f9c8b129e711dfc292b68ee61ea5ab555d2","tid":2463751,"uid":52779,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好貴仲要唔好食"},{"pid":"f16d48d558b01eb6a7a37dc06673619f0f3d75d1","tid":2463751,"uid":264529,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"$160一次私飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acf643e534f40e84c5cdcbf6760d03d65129f57","tid":2463751,"uid":12599,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:11:26.000Z","msg":"俾咁貴食垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d3b590d984fe6dbcd6bea7153689a65bd5efa5","tid":2463751,"uid":70227,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:12:13.000Z","msg":"csd班友都係仆街多"},{"pid":"51dc3302571438f9e378d91890f62262945753ee"